Name: Average resolution time for 'Completed + Resolved' activities.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Resolved and the end of the case

Name: Average delay time before starting 'Completed + Resolved' after 'Accepted + Wait - User'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + Resolved' activities in cases with 'Completed + In Call' preceding it.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time difference between 'Completed + Resolved' and 'Completed + Closed'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Longest duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved'.
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Shortest time to reach 'Completed + Resolved' from any activity.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time spent in 'Completed + Resolved' across all cases.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Resolved and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Resolved' to the next activity.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Resolved and the end of the case

Name: Comparison of average duration between 'Accepted + Assigned' and 'Completed + Resolved' versus 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Resolved' to 'Completed + Closed' in cases without 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Completed + Resolved' in cases following 'Accepted + In Progress'.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time until 'Completed + Resolved' from the start of the case.
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Distribution of time taken for 'Completed + Resolved' by organization country.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time variance analysis for 'Completed + Resolved' across different resources.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Duration analysis of 'Completed + Resolved' in the top 5 longest process variants.
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Resolved' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Cycle time of 'Completed + Resolved' in the context of incident and problem management processes.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Resolved and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time analysis for reaching 'Completed + Resolved' from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in high impact cases.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Comparison of time to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases with and without 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'.
